[div class=p 
	"If you fill an URL here, this URL will be used instead of the regular avatar URL, and you will be given an option to select a "mood" for each of your posts. A 
	[code 
		"$
	]code
	" character in the URL will be replaced by the mood index number for each post.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	[b 
		"Example: 
		[a href=http://site.url/avatar$.png rel=noopener external nofollow 
			"http://site.url/avatar$.png
		]a
		" 
	]b
	$LF
]div
[ul 
	[li 
		" If the URL does not contain 
		[code 
			"$
		]code
		", this setting has no effect.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" This does not generate any new images; it only performs pattern substitution on the URL (replacing 
		[code 
			"$
		]code
		" by a number). You need to provide the images yourself.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
